page.title: 15POPULATION FORRES EAST
page.content: Population in our block is divided between people living in Forres and in the countryside.There are more people living in the urban areas than in the rural areas. Most people live in the housing estates which are{ {Forbeshill,Drumduan}and a small part of {Sanquar.}A small minority of the people live in the surrounding area. Most of the people live in the more modern houses. Some of the people living in the high street live in the oldest houses in the area. The only school in our block has 293 pupils. The population of Forres was about {4169}The population now is over {nine {thousand}and still rising with more housing estates being constructed. Some people in the area work at Ardersier which is a construction building yard in the Moray Firth. The other people work locally.
